text: ยง 11-123 Interest compounded daily. In computing the amount of any interest required to be paid under section 11-224 (except subdivision j thereof), 11-224.1, 11-264, 11-306, 11-307, 11-312, 11-313, 17-151, 19-152, 24-317, 24-512, 24-605, 26-128, 26-517.1, 27-2144 or 27-4029.1 of the code, such interest shall be compounded daily.
